# StatusLine Config

Format: `{branch} {changes} {last_cmd}`

```
[git branch] [±N pending] [last command or _]
```

## Fields

- **Branch**: `git rev-parse --abbrev-ref HEAD`
- **Pending changes**: `git status --porcelain | wc -l` → `+N` if changes, empty if clean
- **Last command**: last 20 chars of the last `exec` command run (truncated)

## Example Output

```
main +3 "ruff check ."
feature/NM-45 +1 "python bot/m~"
```

## Configuration

```json
{
  "format": "{branch} {changes} {last_cmd}",
  "separator": " | ",
  "max_cmd_len": 20,
  "empty_changes": "_",
  "colors": {
    "branch": "#7aa2f7",
    "changes": "#e0af68",
    "clean": "#9ece6a",
    "last_cmd": "#565f89"
  }
}
```
